rooms api:
GET api/rooms/listAllRoomBeds/4 -> query rooms with beds

GET api/rooms/listAllRoom/ -> allRooms(you can query with status or not)
DELETE api/rooms/deleteRoom/4 -> delete room by id
POST api/rooms/createRoom/ -> create room
[PUT/PATCH] api/rooms/updateRoom/<int:id> -> PUT FOR ALL FIELD,PATCH FOR ONE FIELD


dorm api:
GET api/dormitory/listAll/ -> list all dormitory
GET api/dormitory/withRooms/ -> list all dormitory with rooms
POST api/dormitory/createDorm/ -> create Dorm
[PUT/PATCH] api/dormitory/updateDorm/<int:id> -> PUT FOR ALL FIELD,PATCH FOR ONE FIELD


bed api:
GET api/beds/listAll/ -> list all dormitory[you can filter the status]
GET api/beds/getBedById/<int:id> -> get bed by specific id
POST api/beds/createBed/ -> create Dorm
[PUT/PATCH] api/beds/updateBed/<int:id> -> PUT FOR ALL FIELD,PATCH FOR ONE FIELD